desc: Maramataka Māori is the Maori lunar/moon calendar, Matariki stars New Zealand, printed and distributed each year around matariki and Maori new year in New Zealand. Manawhenua is a place where you can find maramataka moon phase journals and Māori moon experts in New Zealand calendars in New Zealand.

layout.text: Welcome, to Maramataka with Heeni Hoterene
